-- Bellzone Mining Signs Guinea Accord for Studies on Rail, Port Facilities
-- Amanda Jordan
-- 2010-06-17T06:07:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/bellzone-mining-signs-guinea-accord-for-studies-on-rail-port-facilities.html

          
          
             Bellzone Mining Plc, an iron-ore
company operating in Guinea, signed an agreement with the
government for the exclusive right to complete technical and
economic feasibility studies for rail and port facilities to
transport iron ore from its Kalia project.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Amanda Jordan in London at 
 ajordan11@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        